    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_3_3768-3868",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3768-3868",
      "markText": "杜甫是中华民族的诗圣，诗圣就是诗国中的圣人。儒家主张个人应该修行进德，争取超凡入圣，孟子说“人皆可以为尧舜”，王阳明的弟子说“满街都是圣人”，杜甫就是从布衣中产生的一位圣贤，我们应该对他怀有敬畏之心。",
      "totalCount": 846,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3768&rangeEnd=3868",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3768&rangeEnd=3868"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_6159-6217",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6159-6217",
      "markText": "我们在现存的慈恩寺塔的题名中还可以找到李商隐的题名。这是我亲眼看到的，李商隐的题名还刻在那里，我看见的时候好激动哦！",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6159&rangeEnd=6217",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6159&rangeEnd=6217"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_3209-3255",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3209-3255",
      "markText": "这首诗见于《南史·曹景宗传》，四句诗是：“去时儿女悲，归来笳鼓竞。借问行路人，何如霍去病？”",
      "totalCount": 576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3209&rangeEnd=3255",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3209&rangeEnd=3255"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_19294-19313",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "19294-19313",
      "markText": "用金圣叹的话说，简直就是“金屎之别”。",
      "totalCount": 533,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=19294&rangeEnd=19313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=19294&rangeEnd=19313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_3_863-947",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "863-947",
      "markText": "我开始觉得天才横溢的李白固然可敬，可他常常“驾鸿凌紫冥”，虽然在云端里“俯视洛阳川”，毕竟与我相去甚远。杜甫却时时在我身边，而且以“蹇驴破帽”的潦倒模样混杂在我辈中间。",
      "totalCount": 494,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=863&rangeEnd=947",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=863&rangeEnd=947"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_23208-23267",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "23208-23267",
      "markText": "认为诗歌的每一句都有直接的政治含义附加在上面，这是汉儒解读《诗经》的方法，这是一种杀死诗歌美的解读方式，我们当然不取。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=23208&rangeEnd=23267",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=23208&rangeEnd=23267"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_31788-31857",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "31788-31857",
      "markText": "你如果想好好地读一遍杜诗的话，那么请你先读《咏怀五百字》，先读《北征》，再读《秋兴八首》《诸将五首》《咏怀古迹五首》，这些都是必读的杜诗。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=31788&rangeEnd=31857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=31788&rangeEnd=31857"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_24686-24770",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "24686-24770",
      "markText": "时代背景固然重要，大背景、小背景、个人的遭遇都很重要，但是更重要的是这个作家的内心世界，是他的才情、他的胸怀、他的见识、他的思想，这些内在的因素也许比外在的因素更重要。",
      "totalCount": 392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24686&rangeEnd=24770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=24686&rangeEnd=24770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_1565-1596",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1565-1596",
      "markText": "几个诗人在同时同地就同一个题目来写诗，这在古代叫“同题共作”。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1565&rangeEnd=1596",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1565&rangeEnd=1596"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_25203-25239",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "25203-25239",
      "markText": "杜甫站的高度比其他诗人更上一层楼，所以唯独杜甫成为那个时代最伟大的诗人。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25203&rangeEnd=25239",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25203&rangeEnd=25239"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_5433-5496",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5433-5496",
      "markText": "我一到西安，首先想的就是去登这个塔，登上去以后很激动：这是杜甫登过的塔啊！杜甫当年就是在这里写下《同诸公登慈恩寺塔》这首诗的！",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5433&rangeEnd=5496",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5433&rangeEnd=5496"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_4878-4943",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4878-4943",
      "markText": "比赛结束以后，沈约对别人说：我是让这个老头子的，我还有三条没说出来，怕他恼羞成怒。后来梁武帝还是知道了，果然大怒，差点把沈约杀了。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4878&rangeEnd=4943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4878&rangeEnd=4943"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_11221-11308",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "11221-11308",
      "markText": "俄国的别林斯基说过：“诗人是社会的晴雨表。”社会的变化，任何细微的变化，应该在诗人笔下得到反映。你既然是一个好诗人，就必然是非常敏锐的；如果感觉很迟钝的话，你就做不了好诗人。",
      "totalCount": 308,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11221&rangeEnd=11308",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=11221&rangeEnd=11308"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_8_23870-23893",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "23870-23893",
      "markText": "诗是中国一切文学的极致，文学最高的境界就是诗。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=23870&rangeEnd=23893",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=23870&rangeEnd=23893"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_20233-20325",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "20233-20325",
      "markText": "这两句为什么不够好呢？你既然登上了一个非常高的高度，视野非常开阔，你看到远处都是青蒙蒙的一片，那么，你看地面的亭台楼阁就不应该是玲珑剔透，不应该看得如此清楚，否则你所在的高度就降低了。",
      "totalCount": 304,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20233&rangeEnd=20325",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20233&rangeEnd=20325"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_43567-43647",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "43567-43647",
      "markText": "诗歌也是一样，杜甫在这里的描写实际上跟韩愈对琴声的描写是出于同一种艺术构思，先把它扬到极点，然后一下子抑到极点，这在文气上就是沉郁顿挫。什么叫顿挫？这就是顿挫。",
      "totalCount": 304,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=43567&rangeEnd=43647",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=43567&rangeEnd=43647"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_15482-15528",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "15482-15528",
      "markText": "大家知道，阮籍因为政治上没有出路，人生没有出路，就随意地到处乱走，走到无路可走了就痛哭一场。",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15482&rangeEnd=15528",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15482&rangeEnd=15528"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_4_9515-9590",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "9515-9590",
      "markText": "创造一个成语谈何容易，但李林甫文化水准低，却创造了一个成语，当然他不是用笔墨写下来的，他是用身体写作，这个成语叫“口蜜腹剑”。口蜜腹剑是李林甫的表现。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9515&rangeEnd=9590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9515&rangeEnd=9590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_3_1133-1181",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1133-1181",
      "markText": "忽然，一个温和、苍老的声音从黑暗中传来：“安得广厦千万间，大庇天下寒士俱欢颜，风雨不动安如山！”",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030663&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1133&rangeEnd=1181",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fa2326c0813ab727ag01329a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1133&rangeEnd=1181"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300030663_3_3471-3541",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3471-3541",
